# Static-host headers (Cloudflare Pages / Netlify read this file from the build output).
# CRITICAL: the COOP+COEP pair gives the page cross-origin isolation, which is REQUIRED
# for SharedArrayBuffer → the bb.js ZK prover. Without these, deposits/sends/withdraws
# silently fail to prove on the deployed site. credentialless (not require-corp) keeps
# WalletConnect/Reown's cross-origin resources working.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless

# Hashed build assets are immutable — cache them hard.
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
